      <num>SEC. 2.210</num>
      <heading>Cooperative purchasing</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The purchasing agent shall have the authority to join with other units of government
               in cooperative purchasing plans when the best interest of the city would be served
               thereby.</p>
        <p>(Ord. No. 7.16, § 1, 5/24/16.)</p>
      </content>
    </section>
